# Public Assets Directory

This directory contains static assets that are served directly.

## Required Files

You should add the following files before deploying:

### Favicon and Icons
- `favicon.ico` - Browser favicon (32x32)
- `icon-192.png` - PWA icon (192x192)
- `icon-512.png` - PWA icon (512x512)

### Open Graph Images
- `og-image.png` - Open Graph image for social sharing (1200x630)

### Other Assets
- Add any images, fonts, or static files here

## Generating Icons

You can use tools like:
- [Favicon Generator](https://favicon.io/)
- [PWA Icon Generator](https://www.pwabuilder.com/)
- [Real Favicon Generator](https://realfavicongenerator.net/)

## Note on Performance

- Keep file sizes small (use WebP/AVIF for images)
- Use next/image for images that need optimization
- Static files in this folder are served as-is
